'''Samuel Attah-Mensah ‘Sammens’''' is a [[Ghanaian people|Ghanaian]] media personality, business man, Managing Director of award-winning [[Accra]]-based English speaking radio station [[Citi FM (Ghana)|Citi FM]]. He is also the Vice President of [[Ghana Independent Broadcasters Association]] (GIBA)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ibagh.org/index.php/about-us/executive-council.html|title=Executive Council|last=admin|website=www.ibagh.org|access-date=2016-07-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/I-would-ve-sacked-this-Adakabre-boy-if-Citi-FM-boss-428704|title=I would've sacked this Adakabre boy if ... - Citi FM boss|website=www.ghanaweb.com|access-date=2016-07-13}}</ref> and a lecturer.

